      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "STAGE 0 — Problem Statement\nDesign Snake & Ladder: N-cell board, players take turns rolling a die,\nmove forward, and snakes/ladders/bombs jump them. First to land EXACTLY on N wins.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STAGE 0 — Problem Statement\nDesign Snake & Ladder: N-cell board, players take turns rolling a die,\nmove forward, and snakes/ladders/bombs jump them. First to land EXACTLY on N wins.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

