      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2005,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 5,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "STAGE 1 — Requirements  (clarify, ~5 min)\n1. Board of N cells; players start at 0\n2. Fair die (1-6)\n3. Multiple players, fixed-order rotation\n4. Cell effects: snake (down) / ladder (up) / bomb (back to 0)\n5. Overshoot past N => stay put (must roll EXACT)\n6. First to land exactly on N wins; game ends\n7. Effects can CHAIN (a jump landing on another jump fires it)\n\nOUT OF SCOPE (say 2-3, then stop): GUI / animation / 2-D rendering,\nnetworked or persistent multiplayer, weighted dice / power-ups.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STAGE 1 — Requirements  (clarify, ~5 min)\n1. Board of N cells; players start at 0\n2. Fair die (1-6)\n3. Multiple players, fixed-order rotation\n4. Cell effects: snake (down) / ladder (up) / bomb (back to 0)\n5. Overshoot past N => stay put (must roll EXACT)\n6. First to land exactly on N wins; game ends\n7. Effects can CHAIN (a jump landing on another jump fires it)\n\nOUT OF SCOPE (say 2-3, then stop): GUI / animation / 2-D rendering,\nnetworked or persistent multiplayer, weighted dice / power-ups.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

