      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "STAGE 2 — Core Entities  (nouns → classes)\nData:      Player (name, currPos)\nWorld:     Board (N, map<cell, CellEffect>) · Dice (roll 1-6)\nBehavior:  CellEffect -> Snake · Ladder · Bomb      (STRATEGY PATTERN)\nContext:   Game  (players, board, dice — runs the turn loop)\n\nNote: a Cell is JUST an index — no Cell objects. Only interesting cells\nlive in a HashMap<Integer, CellEffect>.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STAGE 2 — Core Entities  (nouns → classes)\nData:      Player (name, currPos)\nWorld:     Board (N, map<cell, CellEffect>) · Dice (roll 1-6)\nBehavior:  CellEffect -> Snake · Ladder · Bomb      (STRATEGY PATTERN)\nContext:   Game  (players, board, dice — runs the turn loop)\n\nNote: a Cell is JUST an index — no Cell objects. Only interesting cells\nlive in a HashMap<Integer, CellEffect>.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

