      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PASS 1 — First-go Attributes & Functions  (rough — expect mistakes!)\nCell { type, start, end }  + big if/else in apply()   <- OCP violation!\nBoard { n, map }  addEffect()  movePlayer()\nGame  { players, board, dice }  play()\n\nWHAT'S STILL MISSING (you won't see it yet):\n  · one class with a 'type' + if/else, or SEPARATE effect classes?\n  · apply(int pos)  vs  apply(Player)?   is Player a FIELD or a PARAM?\n  · who rotates the turn?   who applies the effect after a move?\n  · overshoot past N?   winning pos = n  or  n*n?   init the HashMap?",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PASS 1 — First-go Attributes & Functions  (rough — expect mistakes!)\nCell { type, start, end }  + big if/else in apply()   <- OCP violation!\nBoard { n, map }  addEffect()  movePlayer()\nGame  { players, board, dice }  play()\n\nWHAT'S STILL MISSING (you won't see it yet):\n  · one class with a 'type' + if/else, or SEPARATE effect classes?\n  · apply(int pos)  vs  apply(Player)?   is Player a FIELD or a PARAM?\n  · who rotates the turn?   who applies the effect after a move?\n  · overshoot past N?   winning pos = n  or  n*n?   init the HashMap?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

