      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PASS 3 — Code: the last 20% of correctness\nBoard.movePlayer(p, steps):\n   newPos = p.currPos + steps\n   if newPos > n:  print overshoot;  return          // stay put\n   p.setPos(newPos)\n   while map.has(newPos):                             // chain effects\n       map.get(newPos).apply(p)\n       if newPos == p.currPos: break                  // no move => stop (no infinite loop)\n       newPos = p.currPos\n\nGame.playTurn(): pick player -> roll -> board.move -> win? -> rotate idx\nWIN: land EXACTLY on n  (getWinningPos() returns n, NOT n*n)\nCONVENTION: snake start>end (down), ladder start<end (up); no jump onto 0.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PASS 3 — Code: the last 20% of correctness\nBoard.movePlayer(p, steps):\n   newPos = p.currPos + steps\n   if newPos > n:  print overshoot;  return          // stay put\n   p.setPos(newPos)\n   while map.has(newPos):                             // chain effects\n       map.get(newPos).apply(p)\n       if newPos == p.currPos: break                  // no move => stop (no infinite loop)\n       newPos = p.currPos\n\nGame.playTurn(): pick player -> roll -> board.move -> win? -> rotate idx\nWIN: land EXACTLY on n  (getWinningPos() returns n, NOT n*n)\nCONVENTION: snake start>end (down), ladder start<end (up); no jump onto 0.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

