      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "STRATEGY PATTERN (the crux)\n\nBAD — one class, big if/else:\n  apply(pos) {\n    if (SNAKE) ...\n    else if (LADDER) ...\n    else if (BOMB) ...\n  }\n  new effect => EDIT this method\n  (violates Open/Closed)\n\nGOOD — a class per effect:\n  abstract CellEffect {\n    int start, end;\n    apply(Player p) { }\n  }\n  Snake  : setPos(end)   // down\n  Ladder : setPos(end)   // up\n  Bomb   : setPos(0)     // restart\n\n  new effect => NEW class,\n  edits NOTHING existing.\n\nEXTENSIONS (name, don't build):\n  Teleport · SkipTurn · MineField\n  — each is one new subclass.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STRATEGY PATTERN (the crux)\n\nBAD — one class, big if/else:\n  apply(pos) {\n    if (SNAKE) ...\n    else if (LADDER) ...\n    else if (BOMB) ...\n  }\n  new effect => EDIT this method\n  (violates Open/Closed)\n\nGOOD — a class per effect:\n  abstract CellEffect {\n    int start, end;\n    apply(Player p) { }\n  }\n  Snake  : setPos(end)   // down\n  Ladder : setPos(end)   // up\n  Bomb   : setPos(0)     // restart\n\n  new effect => NEW class,\n  edits NOTHING existing.\n\nEXTENSIONS (name, don't build):\n  Teleport · SkipTurn · MineField\n  — each is one new subclass.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
